709
01:01:11,417 --> 01:01:13,367
<i>I haven't had so much fun in a while.</i>

710
01:01:13,367 --> 01:01:16,147
<i>I'm the happiest when I spend time with you.</i>

711
01:01:16,147 --> 01:01:18,367
