712
01:01:18,367 --> 01:01:20,267
<i>Who's your higher-up who told you to stand guard?</i>

713
01:01:20,267 --> 01:01:23,557
<i>I wouldn't be alive if I knew who he was.</i>

714
01:01:23,557 --> 01:01:26,757
<i>- Could it be...
- What's he doing in the room?</i>

715
01:01:26,757 --> 01:01:28,687
<i>Yeojudaek, you looked at me last night, didn't you?</i>

716
01:01:28,687 --> 01:01:30,317
<i>D-Did I?</i>

717
01:01:30,317 --> 01:01:33,897
<i>Young Master Yoon Bok brought a woman!</i>

718
01:01:33,897 --> 01:01:35,967
