- Hello, Lady Se Ryeong.</i>

719
01:01:35,967 --> 01:01:38,137
<i>I asked if that woman is good-looking.</i>

720
01:01:38,137 --> 01:01:41,437
<i>Take this criminal out of the town square immediately!</i>

721
01:01:41,437 --> 01:01:43,487
<i>Hold on! No!</i>

722
01:01:43,487 --> 01:01:45,697
<i>Please, ahjussi!</i>

723
